<bibRefCitation author="Marshall, B. A. &amp; Barker, G. M." box="[970,1258,1405,1431]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" pagination="49 - 113" refId="ref65739" refString="Marshall, B. A. &amp; Barker, G. M. (2007) A revision of New Zealand landsnails of the genus Cytora Kobelt &amp; Mollendorff, 1897 (Mollusca: Gastropoda: Pupinidae). Tuhinga: Records of the Museum of New Zealand Te Papa Tongarewa, 18, 49 - 113." type="journal article" year="2007">Marshall &amp; Barker (2007</bibRefCitation>
: fig. 4C).
</paragraph>
